column1: # Figures in the 1920 and 1923 columns are not readings from King's Parade and have been omitted.
# They are part of a calculation of an estimate for 1920-1923 based on aggregate readings from the Grimsby Abbey Road site.
# The February 1942 figure is identified on the sheet as a part-estimate and has been retained.
# The station continued until 1981 according to MIDAS.
